Package: appfinRcpp
Type: Package
Title: Up-and-out put option price
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Dariusz KÄ™sicki
Maintainer: Dariusz Ceglinska <darek.kesicki@gmail.com>
Description: The package calculates the theoretical price of dup-and-out put option (using Monte Carlo simulation). 
    The algorithm generates a number of price paths defined by user. For each path, if the maximum price 
    is below the barrier price, the payoff is equal to vanilla put option, else the payoff is zero.
